OL,3,CGraduates should repay #10 a week
OL,4,Cunder reformed system, economist says
OL,6,FAll university graduates should repay
OL,7,Fat least #10 a week under a reformed
OL,8,Fstudent loan system, a former
OL,9,Fgovernment adviser has said.
OL,11,FTim Leunig, an economist and an
OL,12,Fadviser to the Treasury and the
OL,13,FDepartment for Education under the
OL,14,FConservatives, has published a 10-
OL,15,Fpoint plan for "fixing" weaknesses in
OL,16,Fthe student finance system in England.
