OL,3,CGraduates should repay #10 a week
OL,4,Cunder reformed system, economist says
OL,6,FIn a paper published by the Higher
OL,7,FEducation Policy Institute (Hepi)
OL,8,Fthink tank, Mr Leunig has called for
OL,9,Fthe "absurd" 40-year repayment term on
OL,10,Fstudent loans to be cut to 20 years,
OL,11,Fand the debt should never rise.
OL,13,FMr Leunig, who is a visiting professor
OL,14,Fat the London School of Economics
OL,15,F(LSE), said all graduates should have
OL,16,Fto repay at least #10 a week "no
OL,17,Fmatter their income" to make the
OL,18,Fsystem more financially stable.
