OL,3,CGraduates should repay #10 a week
OL,4,Cunder reformed system, economist says
OL,6,FUniversity leaders have warned of
OL,7,Fsignificant financial concerns as a
OL,8,Fresult of frozen tuition fees paid by
OL,9,Fdomestic students and a drop in
OL,10,Foverseas students.
OL,12,FThe previous government raised the cap
OL,13,Fon university tuition fees in England
OL,14,Fto #9,000 a year in 2012, but it has
OL,15,Fbeen fixed at #9,250 since 2017.
