OL,3,CGraduates should repay #10 a week
OL,4,Cunder reformed system, economist says
OL,6,FEarlier this month, Universities UK
OL,7,F(UUK) suggested that students should
OL,8,Fpay higher tuition fees and more
OL,9,Ftaxpayers' cash is needed to tackle a
OL,10,Ffunding black hole in England's
OL,11,Funiversities.
OL,13,FOther proposals in the paper by the
OL,14,Feconomist include a 1% "surcharge"
OL,15,Fpayable by employers when they hire a
OL,16,Fgraduate and new maintenance grants of
OL,17,Faround #11,000 for students whose
OL,18,Ffamilies have incomes below #25,000.
