OL,6,FProfessor Eric Neumayer, deputy
OL,7,Fpresident and vice-chancellor at LSE,
OL,8,Fsaid: "Tim Leunig provides a costed
OL,9,Fand principled proposal for radically
OL,10,Freforming the current system of
OL,11,Fstudent finance.
OL,13,F"One may quibble with some of the
OL,14,Fdetails he puts forward, but one
OL,15,Fcannot argue with the fact that
OL,16,Fstudent finance in its current form is
OL,17,Fbroken and leaves all stakeholders
OL,18,Fdissatisfied.
